# Keep the Docker build context small + correct. The Dockerfiles install deps
# and generate the Prisma client fresh inside the build, so nothing installed
# or generated locally should leak in (it would only slow the COPY and risk a
# host/container arch mismatch).
**/node_modules
.git
.github
out
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/generated
**/coverage

# Never bake local env / secrets into an image layer.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Editor / OS noise.
.vscode
.idea
.DS_Store
*.log
